Hello <%= @email %>,

Re: <%= @subject %>

WELCOME TO POSTCARDMAILER.US!

Here's how to use our service:

1. SIGN UP
   - Send an email to signup@postcardmailer.us
   - Include your full name in the subject line
   - Include your mailing address in the body

   Example:
   To: signup@postcardmailer.us
   Subject: John Smith
   Body: 123 Main St, Apt 4B
         San Francisco, CA 94110

2. ADD AN ADDRESS
   - Send an email to adduser@postcardmailer.us
   - Include a nickname for this address in the subject line
   - Include the recipient's name and address in the body

   Example:
   To: adduser@postcardmailer.us
   Subject: mom
   Body: Jane Smith
         456 Oak Avenue
         Chicago, IL 60601

3. SEND A POSTCARD
   - Send an email to $nickname@postcardmailer.us
   - Use the subject line for the message to the recipient
   - Attach the image you want to use for the postcard

   Example:
   To: mom@postcardmailer.us
   Subject: Had a great time in San Francisco!
   Attachment: vacation-photo.jpg

4. GET HELP
   - Send an email to help@postcardmailer.us anytime for these instructions 